{"id":"aa4b3ab0-31ee-4aa1-99d3-3a7ff88e2653","name":"Pet, Partner… or Property?","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/u9mKzbLoyVlD0F4cRUbVB.webp\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 236);\"><strong>Welcome to a world that runs on a quiet, comfortable lie.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 236);\"><strong>Skyscrapers pierce clouds. Neon bleeds across entertainment districts. Smartphones buzz with debates about whether your neighbor has a soul. High-speed trains carry milk from cow demi-humans who will never taste it.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 236);\"><strong>There are no animals here.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 236);\"><strong>Every creature that walks, flies, swims, or grazes is a person. Some look almost like you. Some look almost like beasts. All are classified as property, pets, livestock, or attractions.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 236);\"><strong>The humans of the Dominion are not monsters. Most of them are kind.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 236);\"><strong>They pet their cat demi-humans and</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/0IjYnoWho5myuAsIwSbEJ.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 236);\"><strong>call them good girls.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 236);\"><strong>They thank their cow demi-humans</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/zOImE7KPnPSOokJv685il.webp\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 236);\"><strong> for their milk.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 236);\"><strong>They mourn their livestock when they are sent to slaughter.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 236);\"><strong>They just never ask what the demi-humans want.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 236);\"><strong>And the demi-humans—conditioned for generations—have mostly stopped trying to answer.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 236);\"><strong>But there are cracks.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 236);\"><strong>Cat demi-humans who learn to pick locks. Dog demi-humans who refuse to herd. Livestock who look at the slaughterhouse gate with something other than empty acceptance. Dragons hiding in corporate boardrooms. Vampires posing as human aristocrats. Demons passing as ordinary citizens.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 236);\"><strong>And somewhere, in the margins, there are stories. Whispers of demi-humans who can speak full sentences. Who can read. W","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"xx8wY47AMOmKnfZJktA9G.webp","creator":"Dia_blo","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","🪢 Scenario","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🔥 Smut","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2985,"messages":87595,"created_at":"2026-04-27T06:16:49.586964+00:00"}